metadata.name: "Life" by Civilized Villagrr #1/10
metadata.description: "LIFE" is Civilized Villagrr's submission for Immortal Africa: LIFE. Immortal Africa is the first commissioned pan-African digital art collection. 100% of primary sales and 100% of royalties go to the artist. Find more art from Civilized Villagrr @cvlizedvillagrr and https://linktr.ee/civilizedvillagrr
